12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 11 O.S. 2021, Section 50-109, as
14 last amended by Section 3, Chapter 357, O.S.L. 2024 (11 O.S. Supp.
15 2025, Section 50-109), is amended to read as follows:
16 Section 50-109. Any municipality participating in the Oklahoma
17 Police Pension and Retirement System shall appropriate funds, for
18 the use and benefit of the System, as provided in the following
19 schedule:
20 1. Prior to July 1, 1991, a minimum of ten percent (10%) of the
21 actual paid base salary of each member of the System employed by the
22 municipality;
23
24
